using Interquartile Range(IQR)¶

  • H-Spread/Mid_spread
  • Measures the statistical dispersion/spread
  • IQR = Quantile 3(75) - Quantile 1(25)
In [51]:
q1 = df.quantile(0.25)
q3 = df.quantile(0.75)
In [52]:
IQR = q3 - q1

       'anorexia', 'liver_big', 'liver_firm', 'spleen_palpable', 'spiders',

In [64]:
# using Skbest
skb = SelectKBest(score_func=chi2,k=10)
